title_full:
Various Artists

              —
              Buganda Royal Music Revival
            
              (Nyege Nyege Tapes)
label: Nyege Nyege Tapes
description:
Collecting archival recordings and presenting them alongside studio material from 2019, "Bugandan Royal Music Revival" provides a valuable potted history of Bugandan court music. It's stunning work, showcasing the different instruments, styles and techniques that remain the backbone of Uganda's traditional culture.

              (Planet Mu Records Ltd.)
label: Planet Mu Records Ltd.
description:
Sasu Ripatti (Vladislav Delay, Luomo et al) drops his most satisfying set in ages, folding rap and footwork influences into buzzing, rhythmic fog banks of chopped vocals, rattling snares and wobbling subs. "Fun Is Not A Straight Line" is to hip-hop what "Vocalcity" was to house >> proper.
